commits.message: mariadb: rename run.sh into docker-entrypoint.sh and make it executable
mariadb: make docker-entrypoint.sh write to stderr
mariadb: use test command '[[' instead of '['
mariadb: do not run pre-exec and pre-init scripts
mariadb: do not leave params in docker-compose.yml blank

mariadb: install mariadb-server-utils

For upgrading from MariaDB 10.5 to MariaDB 10.6.

pull_request.title: Keep MariaDB up to date (upgrade it to 10.6)

repo.name: mmb
repo.description: Set of Dockerfiles and assets related to them for building Docker images with different services

repo.name: mmb
repo.description: Set of Dockerfiles and assets related to them for building Docker images with different services

comment.diff_hunk:
@@ -1,13 +1,11 @@
-version: "2"
+version: "3.8"
 services:
   mariadb:
-    image: cusdeb/mariadb:10.5-amd64
+    image: cusdeb/mariadb:10.6-amd64
     network_mode: "host"
     environment:
     - MYSQLD_port=${MYSQLD_port}
     - MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=cusdeb
-    - MYSQL_DATABASE=
-    - MYSQL_USER=
-    - MYSQL_PASSWORD=
-    volumes:
-    - /srv/mysql:/var/lib/mysql
comment.body: Нет, этот docker-compose.yml играет роль примера. Реально образ используется в MediaWiki и Nextcloud'е.
